#
# Source clusters:
#   - Dhoruba bin Wahad (Richard Moore) - Panther 21 + 1971 BLA-attributed
#     attempted murder of NYPD officers; 19 years in NY state prison; 1990
#     release after COINTELPRO Brady evidence revealed
#   - Ericka Huggins + New Haven Black Panther trial (1969 Alex Rackley
#     case; jury hung 10-2 for acquittal May 1971)
#   - SLA non-Olson (James Kilgore, Bill Harris, Emily Harris/Montague,
#     Michael Bortin) - 2003 plea on the April 1975 Carmichael bank
#     robbery in which Myrna Opsahl was killed
#   - Russell Means - AIM co-founder; multiple South Dakota state and
#     federal prosecutions; Wounded Knee 1973 federal charges dismissed
#     for FBI misconduct September 1974
#
